22/* Specification. */
23#include "read-po.h"

25#include "po-lex.h"
26#include "po-gram.h"
27
28/* Read a .po / .pot file from a stream, and dispatch to the various
29 abstract_catalog_reader_class_ty methods. */
30static void
31po_parse (abstract_catalog_reader_ty *this, FILE *fp,
32 const char *real_filename, const char *logical_filename)
33{
34 lex_start (fp, real_filename, logical_filename);
35 po_gram_parse ();
36 lex_end ();
37}
38
39const struct catalog_input_format input_format_po =
40{
41 po_parse, /* parse */
42 false /* produces_utf8 */
43};
